msgctxt "68_Ajikawa"
msgid "Akiyama-san! I went to Kyushu No. 1 Star, as you suggested."
msgstr "¡Akiyama-san! Fui a Kyushu Estrella N° 1, como me sugeriste."

msgctxt "80_Ajikawa"
msgid "The pork ramen was outstanding, and the topping accented the\\r\n"\n"soup perfectly. It was the crown jewel of ramen shops!"
msgstr "El ramen de cerdo era extraordinario, los ingredientes combinaban con\\r\n"\n"la sopa perfectamente. ¡Fue la joya de la corona de los locales de ramen!"

msgctxt "92_Akiyama"
msgid "I'm glad you liked it."
msgstr "Me alegra que te haya gustado."

msgctxt "104_Ajikawa"
msgid "I can't wait to include it in our gourmet guide. Here. It's\\r\n"\n"not much, just a token of my thanks."
msgstr "No puedo esperar a incluirlo en nuestra, guía de gourmet. Toma,\\r\n"\n"no es mucho, pero es una pequeña muestra de mi agradecimiento."

msgctxt "140_Ajikawa"
msgid "Akiyama-san! I just went to the ramen shop you suggested."
msgstr "¡Akiyama-san! Fui al local de ramen, como me sugeriste."

msgctxt "152_Ajikawa"
msgid "They did indeed have some delicious ramen. It wasn't exactly\\r\n"\n"as you described, and the owner got a little upset when I\\r\n"\n"talked to him."
msgstr "Sin duda, ellos hacían un ramen delicioso. Aunque no era exactamente\\r\n"\n"como me lo describiste, y el dueño se molestó un poco\\r\n"\n"cuando quise hablarle."

msgctxt "164_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh? I hope I didn't get you in trouble."
msgstr "¿Eh? Espero no haberte metido en un aprieto."

msgctxt "176_Ajikawa"
msgid "Oh, no, the place is definitely guidebook material, so I'm\\r\n"\n"grateful. Here's a token of my thanks."
msgstr "Ah, no, el lugar tiene mucho material para una guía, así que estoy\\r\n"\n"agradecido. Toma una muestra de mi gratitud."

msgctxt "212_Ajikawa"
msgid "Oh, Akiyama-san. I tried stopping by the ramen shop you\\r\n"\n"recommended."
msgstr "Ah, Akiyama-san. Intente buscar el local de ramen\\r\n"\n"que recomendaste."

msgctxt "224_Ajikawa"
msgid "I found what looked like the right place, but when I asked\\r\n"\n"about the soup, the owner suddenly exploded with anger..."
msgstr "Encontré un lugar que parecía el correcto, pero cuando pregunte\\r\n"\n"sobre la sopa, el dueño de repente exploto de ira..."

msgctxt "236_Ajikawa"
msgid "I wonder if I said something wrong? The man chased me out\\r\n"\n"into the street before I tried even one bite of my ramen..."
msgstr "Me pregunto si habré dicho algo malo. El hombre me echo a la calle\\r\n"\n"antes de que pudiese siquiera probar un poquito del ramen..."

msgctxt "248_Akiyama"
msgid "I guess I didn't really do my homework on that one. Sorry\\r\n"\n"about that..."
msgstr "Supongo que fui descuidado y no hice mi tarea bien esta vez.\\r\n"\n"Lo siento..."

msgctxt "260_Ajikawa"
msgid "Oh, I almost forgot... This is my thanks for your help."
msgstr "Ah, casi lo olvido... Esto es una muestra de mi agradecimiento."

msgctxt "296_Ajikawa"
msgid "Anyway, Akiyama-san, I really want to thank you for all of\\r\n"\n"your help."
msgstr "En fin, Akiyama-san, Realmente quiero agradecerte por\\r\n"\n"toda tu ayuda."

msgctxt "308_Akiyama"
msgid "I hope at least some of the info proves useful."
msgstr "Espero que la información te haya sido de utilidad."

msgctxt "320_Ajikawa"
msgid "Yes, your tips got me well on my way to writing the\\r\n"\n"gourmet's guide to Kamurocho."
msgstr "Sí, tus consejos me llevarán por el buen camino para\\r\n"\n"escribir la guía gourmet de Kamurocho."

msgctxt "344_Ajikawa"
msgid "In fact, as far as yakiniku and ramen go, I may just include\\r\n"\n"your recommendations word for word."
msgstr "Incluso, en lo que se refiere al yakiniku y ramen, podría\\r\n"\n"escribir tus recomendaciones palabra por palabra."

msgctxt "356_Ajikawa"
msgid "I'd like to thank you for all you've done. Please, take\\r\n"\n"this."
msgstr "Me gustaría agradecerte todo lo que has hecho.\\r\n"\n"Por favor, acepta esto."

msgctxt "392_Akiyama"
msgid "But this is pretty valuable, isn't it? Now I feel bad."
msgstr "Pero esto es demasiado caro. Ahora me siento un poco mal."

msgctxt "404_Ajikawa"
msgid "I'm off to sniff out more of Kamurocho's culinary gems!\\r\n"\n"Farewell!"
msgstr "¡Ahora me iré a olfatear unas cuantas joyas culinarias de\\r\n"\n"Kamurocho más! ¡Adiós!"

